This is the code of computing 2D Minkowski Functionals for spherical density maps,
such as CMB or weak lensing convergence maps, in the HEALPix format.

CFITSIO Library is necessary.

After adding an appropriate CFITIO library path to Makefile, type
make

You can do a test calculation by  
make test

References:
 C. Hikage, E. Komatsu, T. Matsubara, ApJ 653 (2006), 11-26
 C. Hikage, T. Matsubara, P. Coles, M. Liguori, F. K. Hansen, S. Matarrese, MNRAS 389 (2008), 1439-1446
